## 📊 数据流设计

### WebSocket 实时数据流

```mermaid
sequenceDiagram
    participant UI as Vue 组件
    participant Store as Pinia Store
    participant WS as WebSocket Client
    participant Server as 后端服务
    participant Agent as Agent 系统

    UI->>Store: 调用 action
    Store->>WS: 发送 WebSocket 消息
    WS->>Server: WebSocket 传输
    Server->>Agent: 触发 Agent 状态变化

    Agent->>Server: 状态更新通知
    Server->>WS: 推送实时事件
    WS->>Store: 触发事件处理
    Store->>Store: 更新 state
    Store->>UI: 响应式更新 UI

    Note over UI,Agent: 实时延迟 < 500ms
```

### REST API 数据流

```mermaid
sequenceDiagram
    participant UI as Vue 组件
    participant API as API Service
    participant HTTP as Axios Client
    participant Server as 后端服务
    participant DB as SQLite 数据库

    UI->>API: 调用 API 方法
    API->>HTTP: 发送 HTTP 请求
    HTTP->>Server: REST API 调用
    Server->>DB: 查询数据
    DB->>Server: 返回数据
    Server->>HTTP: JSON 响应
    HTTP->>API: 返回数据
    API->>UI: 更新组件状态

    Note over UI,DB: API 响应 < 100ms (P99)
